snippet.title: Tetris Battle Gaiden (Super Famicom) Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Tetris Battle Gaiden (テトリス武闘外伝) is a competitive tetris game with crazy power-ups for the Super Famicom (Super Nintendo), released in Japan in 1993. I'm playing single-player on the default difficulty (Easy) with the electrical pink bunny thing.

I'm playing on the mednafen emulator, recorded with OBS. #longplay
